<script>
export default {
  name: 'ShowProject',
  data() {
    return {
      projectName: ''
    };
  },
  methods: {
    fetchProjectData() {
      const query = encodeURIComponent(this.projectName);
      const url = `http://localhost:8000/Projects/searchproject/?project_name=${query}`;

      fetch(url)
        .then(response => response.json())
        .then(data => {
          console.log('Fetched project data:', data);
        })
        .catch(error => {
          console.error('Error fetching project data:', error);
        });
    }
  }
}
</script>
